PrecisAmendments to the EXPORT PERMITS REGULATIONS (SOFTWOOD LUMBER PRODUCTS) providing for the assignment by the Minister of export levels to exporters, taking into account the exporters' recent and present performance in exporting softwood lumber products to the United States and anticipated growth in exports as a result of new production capacity for softwood lumber products.

precis:
Amendments to the EXPORT PERMITS REGULATIONS (SOFTWOOD LUMBER PRODUCTS)
providing for the assignment by the Minister of export levels to exporters,
taking into account the exporters' recent and present performance in
exporting softwood lumber products to the United States and anticipated
growth in exports as a result of new production capacity for softwood
lumber products.
